author: DamiLee
description: In the next decade, NASA, ESA, China, Russia, and Japan all plan to build the first lunar habitats. From origami-style modules to colonies inside lava tubes, these designs push the limits of architecture—and humanity. The real question isn’t just can we live on the Moon, but how we’ll make it feel like home. What would your Moon home look like?
title: What do you think “home” would feel like in space?
